f our board in march  he has served as senior vice president supply chain management at walgreen co one of the nations largest drugstore chains and part of the retail pharmacy usa division of walgreens boots alliance inc since may  prior to joining walgreens mr slone served as executive vice president supply chain and general manager of services for officemax inc a provider of office products business machines and related items printforpay services and office furniture from  to  prior to officemax mr slone held various supply chain leadership positions with whirlpool corporation general motors company and federalmogul holdings corporation he also held prior consulting positions with electronic data systems corporation and ernst  young he authored leading a supply chain turnaround and coauthored are you the weakest link in your companys supply chain articles published in the october  and september  issues of the harvard business review respectively in may  harvard business press published the book entitled the new supply chain agenda the  steps that drive real value which was coauthored by mr slone mr slone is a supply chain thought leader mr slones supply chain expertise his retail and automotive industry experience and his experience in change management are expected to provide valuable insights to our board as we evaluate and work to optimize our supply chain source advance auto parts inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view reuben e slones full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like reuben e slone more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in reuben e slones network and community follow changes in reuben e slones employment and moneyinmotion connect with reuben e slone through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example reuben e slone reuben e slones connections  sign up now to view reuben e slones  connect